txt.en: <rgb=#FF0000>Roar</rgb> to shoo rabbits in the fields ([placeholder]/[placeholder])
'Pesky rabbits are eating some of vegetables from the fields. Might you shoo them away? Do not hurt the rabbits though. While they are prized vegetables, they are still only just vegetables!'
When neighbours work together, the households of the Rohan Kingstead will glisten upon the rolling plains.
Rabbits can be found throughout the neighbourhoods of the Rohan Kingstead.\n\nYou should shoo rabbits out of the gardens.
